	<p>Photography is going through an exciting transition period as many film photographers are beginning to explore the new capabilities of digital cameras. While the fundamentals have remained similar, other aspects are markedly different. This is a great time to get involved with digital photography.</p>
	<p>These tutorials are rarely influenced by changes in image editing software and camera equipment -- due to their unique concept-based approach. Most tutorials therefore apply to both compact and digital SLR cameras. So, don't be afraid to dig deeper! You'll be sure to find what you need regardless of the camera you've purchased.</p>

